# Production environment variables
#
# The production build is served by the layercake binary same-origin with the
# API, so VITE_API_BASE_URL is intentionally unset — endpoints resolve against
# window.location.origin. Only set it if you deliberately host the static
# frontend separately from the API.

# NODE_ENV is injected by the bundler; avoid overriding it here to keep Vite happy.
